title: Adobe Creative Suite 6
description:
Adobe Creative Suite 6
======================

This torrent consists of the installer for the master 
collection version 6 and the corresponding 
'amtlib.dll' file for each available product in CS6.

It contains the following files:

* ACS6.zip
* info.txt
* Adobe-Creative-Suite-6--md5-list.chks

This is how you install the master collection and make 
all products available:

- Extract 'ACS6.zip'
- Run 'MasterCollection_CS6_LS16.exe'
- Use the files from 'Files/' on the corresponding 
  product

You can check the files using md5sum like this:

$ md5sum -c ./Adobe-Creative-Suite-6--md5-list.chks

Or just compare the md5 checksums you generate from the
 downloaded files to these (same order as above):

* 023d935c17ade931fcdd1ea6a7b91abb
* 12bb777f10a0147f923fa7b9b16fa87e
   This last one (of 'info.txt') can be different

Thanks for downloading 'Adobe Creative Suite 6' and
 keep seeding! :)
